# Sliding Window TDA Demo

Takens embedding of a 1D periodic signal (sine wave) and persistent homology on the resulting point cloud.```


Cell 1:
```
## 1. Generate periodic signal```


Cell 2:
```
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

np.random.seed(42)
t = np.linspace(0, 20, 1000)
signal = np.cos(5 * t)  # periodic with period 2*pi/5

plt.figure(figsize=(10, 3))
plt.plot(t, signal)
plt.xlabel('Time')
plt.ylabel('Amplitude')
plt.title('Periodic signal: cos(5t)')
plt.show()```


